{"tid":645453,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳中超隊以全球最高薪誘雲加","createTime":"2018-04-28T06:56:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T07:06:22.000Z","uid":46892,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c399b8010c4a7332ea791acb02bb31d04abf111b","tid":645453,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T06:56:05.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=tbLlw32qYTf03B9dS5lvQywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=8cd53d27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】雲加宣佈季後離開阿仙奴後，下個目的地眾說紛紜，最近有指中超球隊開出全球最高教練人工利誘他加盟。<br />\n<br />\n根據英國《鏡報》報道，雲加（Arsene Wenger）在宣佈即將離開執教了22年的阿仙奴後，已收到多份聘書，當中以來自中超的球會出手最為豪氣，要是這名68歲老帥首肯，將會成為全球最高薪教練。<br />\n<br />\n意大利名帥納比執教中國國家隊，年薪為2400萬鎊，而雲加入主中超球隊後，人工會更高，而他現時於阿仙奴每年只賺800萬鎊；至於英超最高薪領隊為曼城的哥迪奧拿，1年人工有1600萬鎊。<br />\n<br />\n不過，據知雲加屬意執教法國或西班牙球會，相信以巴黎聖日耳門的機會最高，因為他們財力雄厚之餘，主帥艾美利剛在周五宣佈將於球季結束後離任。"},{"pid":"dda52df39ac61e5e9ee41c9bdecc7110e0ac58b4","tid":645453,"uid":166785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T06:57:43.000Z","msg":"竟然要去中超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雲加值得更好"},{"pid":"d9724e59d5cfd1f4e72ef7b5f8b5840ee3d08865","tid":645453,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/182455_d108a8ab1d79ac167095243a5d82bf22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F182455_d108a8ab1d79ac167095243a5d82bf22.jpg&h=4313b2fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c281928b846501dbbff47baa5df8a3f0ddc67d8","tid":645453,"uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d9724e59d5cfd1f4e72ef7b5f8b5840ee3d08865","tid":645453,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:02:4